
=Bio=

"I am a Greek architect and PhD candidate, currently working on sharing culture and the urban commons. My research focuses on how sharing and collective practices within cities are affected by physical space as well as other influencing factors. I am working on a selection of cases studies from different cities, and always looking for more!

The commons and how they relate to urban autonomy has been a great interest of mine and along with friends we organized an international conference (AUTONOMA, Towards the Collective City) this past July in Athens, you can find more information here: http://www.autonoma.gr/. The dicscussions that arose in the conference were great and we are now trying to put together the publication. "


